---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Larry SMS Hub Case Study">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/case-studies" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to case studies</a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-1">Building Larry SMS Hub</h1>
    <div class="text-[12px] text-gray-500 mb-3">Case Study • 2025</div>
    <p class="text-gray-600 md:w-3/4 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.9">How I built an SMS automation platform that helps Ghanaian businesses communicate with their customers effectively.</p>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">The Problem</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          Small businesses in Ghana were struggling to communicate with their customers effectively. 
          They needed to send promotional messages, appointment reminders, and updates, but existing solutions were either too expensive or too complex.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700" style="line-height: 1.8">
          Most businesses were manually sending SMS messages or using expensive enterprise solutions that didn't fit their needs or budget.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">The Solution</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          I built Larry SMS Hub as a simple, affordable SMS automation platform that allows businesses to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2 list-disc ml-5" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <li>Send bulk SMS messages to their customers</li>
          <li>Schedule messages for specific times</li>
          <li>Use pre-built templates for common messages</li>
          <li>Import contacts from CSV files</li>
          <li>Track delivery status and responses</li>
          <li>Pay only for what they use (pay-as-you-go)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Technical Approach</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Backend</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Node.js API with Express framework</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Node.js</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Express</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">MongoDB</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">SMS Integration</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Multiple SMS providers for reliability</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">SMS API</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Webhook</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Queue System</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Frontend</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Simple web interface for easy use</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">HTML/CSS</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">JavaScript</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Bootstrap</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700 mb-2">Heroku for hosting and reliability</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1 text-[11px]">
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Heroku</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">MongoDB Atlas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Key Features Built</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Pay-as-You-Go Pricing</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            No monthly fees. Users only pay for SMS messages they send, starting from as low as 2 cedis.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Message Templates</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Pre-built templates for common business messages like promotions, reminders, and announcements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">CSV Import</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Easy contact management by importing customer lists from CSV files.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Scheduled Messages</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Schedule messages to be sent at specific times, perfect for marketing campaigns and reminders.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Delivery Tracking</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">
            Track message delivery status and get reports on successful sends and failures.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Challenges & Learnings</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <strong>SMS Provider Reliability:</strong> Different SMS providers have different delivery rates and costs. I had to integrate multiple providers for better reliability.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <strong>User Education:</strong> Many users weren't familiar with SMS automation concepts. I had to build a simple, intuitive interface.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <strong>Cost Management:</strong> SMS costs can add up quickly. I implemented a pay-as-you-go model to make it affordable for small businesses.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <strong>Key Learning:</strong> Simplicity is key. The most successful features were the ones that required the least explanation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-3">Current Status</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-4">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3" style="line-height: 1.8">
          Larry SMS Hub is live and serving customers. Current features include:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-1 list-disc ml-5" style="line-height: 1.8">
          <li>Bulk SMS sending with delivery tracking</li>
          <li>Message templates and scheduling</li>
          <li>CSV contact import</li>
          <li>Pay-as-you-go pricing starting from 2 cedis</li>
          <li>Simple web interface for easy use</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="/projects/larry-sms-hub" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">View Project</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">All Projects</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Ask Questions</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
<Footer />
